                &none       &kp GRAVE   &kp ESC     &none       &none           &none       &kp HOME    &kp PG_UP   &kp BSPC    &none  
                &kp CAPS    &kp TAB     &none       &none       &none           &kp LEFT    &kp DOWN    &kp UP      &kp RIGHT   &kp RET
    &trans      &none       &none       &none       &none       &none           &none       &kp END     &kp PG_DN   &none       &none       &trans 
                                        &trans      &to NRS2    &kp SPACE       &kp BSPC    &to SYM2    &to BASE 
