//                                     ┗━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┛   ┗━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┛
bindings = <
// ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷   ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷

                &kp N1      &kp N2      &kp N3      &kp N4      &kp N5          &kp N6      &kp N7      &kp N8      &kp N9      &kp N0
                &mt LCTRL COLON &mt LALT RPAR &mt LCMD LBRC &mt LSHFT LBKT &kp G &kp M      &mt RSHFT RBKT &mt RCMD RBRC &mt RALT RPAR &mt RCTRL SEMI
    &trans      &kp GRAVE   &kp TILD    &kp BSLH    &kp LT      &kp EQUAL       &kp PLUS    &kp GT      &kp QMARK   &kp COMMA   &kp PERIOD  &trans 
                                        &kp GLOBE   &mo_sl ALPH ALPH &lt CTR4 SPACE &lt CTR5 BSPC &mo_sl ALPH ALPH  &to BASE
